something. We rarely had to med, and even made decent xp out of it, as well as a couple hundred plat in about an hour of doing this. Very fun, I highly recommend any 40ish wizard with a monk/rogue friend give this a shot!<br>
<br>
-Chiriko, lvl 42 wizard, Innoruuk <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utotenkopftz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TotenkopfTZ</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://freepages.ugo.com/totenkopftz/files/totenk.jpg Width=20 Height=20 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/27/01 9:48:54 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://freepages.ugo.com/Totenkopftz/files/Totenk2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Make money fast! ;)</span><hr size=1> I've never done this on HGs but it is a tactic I've used before with a ranger as a partner. He would snare, I would nuke and just back up with SoW on while he beat the crap out of it aggro's him I just drop another conflag on it.<br>
<br>
